said to be the moment when you

00:00:23.570 --> 00:00:28.220 align:middle line:84%
realize you're in prison, the
moment when you experience

00:00:28.220 --> 00:00:32.150 align:middle line:84%
another reality, the moment when
you see there are other ways

00:00:32.150 --> 00:00:34.147 align:middle line:90%
of looking at it all.

00:00:34.147 --> 00:00:36.230 align:middle line:84%
I'm not talking about other
places in your thought

00:00:36.230 --> 00:00:37.580 align:middle line:90%
process--

00:00:37.580 --> 00:00:39.500 align:middle line:90%
but other.

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:42.620 align:middle line:84%
Now what you call
that place from which

00:00:42.620 --> 00:00:46.610 align:middle line:84%
you look at your life
when before you were just

00:00:46.610 --> 00:00:51.080 align:middle line:84%
busy thinking you were
it, your incarnation life,

00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:53.540 align:middle line:90%
where do you look at it from?

00:00:53.540 --> 00:00:56.880 align:middle line:84%
